<section id="faq" class="section">
  <div class="container faq">
    <div class="kicker">FAQ</div>
    <h2 class="h2">Photoshoot & Delivery</h2>

    <div class="grid section-tight">

      <div class="item">
        <div class="q">How long does photo delivery take? <span>+</span></div>
        <div class="a">Edited photos are delivered within 3–5 days. Video edits may take 5–7 days.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <div class="q">Will I receive raw files? <span>+</span></div>
        <div class="a">Raw files can be purchased as an add-on.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <div class="q">Can I reschedule my shoot? <span>+</span></div>
        <div class="a">Yes — rescheduling is allowed within 24 hours notice.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <div class="q">Do I own full rights to the photos? <span>+</span></div>
        <div class="a">Personal use rights are included. Commercial licensing is available as an add-on.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>




